OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with showery rain in the
OL,6,Fsouth at first otherwise dry with
OL,7,Fbright spells. Further cloud and rain
OL,8,Fwill spread northeast from the
OL,9,Fafternoon becoming heavy at times in
OL,10,Fthe south later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain, this heavy in the south. The
OL,14,Fbest of any drier spells will be in
OL,15,Fthe northeast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,18,Fat first. This soon clears to bright
OL,19,Fspells with the odd afternoon shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
